live. The Magistrate, Mrs Batula Dauda, order that the defendant be remanded in a correctional centre and adjourned the case till Feb. 25, for further mention. (NAN) An Ikeja Chief Magistrates’ Court has remanded a 25-year-old man, Wasiu Nurudeen, for allegedly allowing his friend to rape a teenager in his apartment. Nurudeen, a labourer, who resides at 10, Asoge St., Ijeshatedo in Lagos State, is facing a charge of being an accessory to the commission of a… July 23, 2020 In "News" An Ado-Ekiti Magistrates’ Court on Monday remanded a 60-year-old man, Samuel Orji, in prison over alleged rape of a 12-year-old minor. April 8, 2019 In "News" An Ado-Ekiti Chief Magistrates’ Court on Thursday, remanded Tobi Aremu ,23 in prison Custody over an alleged rape of a 5-year September 22, 2016 In "News"